165
00:07:35,464 --> 00:07:36,404
and jumping for years,

166
00:07:36,904 --> 00:07:38,184
but the player is being asked to do this

167
00:07:38,204 --> 00:07:39,105
for the very first time.

168
00:07:41,164 --> 00:07:43,505
